// Shape Network shaping (kernel-level). Includes optional `transport_fault`
// for nftables drop/reject — a layer-correct home since these share
// the nftables/tc plumbing with rate / delay / loss.
//
// Patching with non-null replaces wholesale; setting `shape: null`
// clears all shaping.
